      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i'm studying for my econ midterm and im a bit stuck. can u give me a real world example of opportunity cost? like if a company has to choose between buying new factory machinery or spending that same money on a big marketing campaign, how would u explain the opportunity cost there?",
